org.jvnet.jax_ws_commons.dime.codec
Class DimeStreamReader

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.xml.ws.util.xml.XMLStreamReaderFilter
      org.jvnet.jax_ws_commons.dime.codec.DimeStreamReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.sun.xml.ws.api.streaming.XMLStreamReaderFactory.RecycleAware, javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamConstants, javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamReader, org.jvnet.staxex.XMLStreamReaderEx
public class DimeStreamReader
extends com.sun.xml.ws.util.xml.XMLStreamReaderFilter
implements org.jvnet.staxex.XMLStreamReaderEx

Parse a SOAP message into a data model and resolve references to attachments. This class is a filter for a standard XMLStreamReader and adds custom behavior for attachments.

Any XML element with a href attribute who's value matches the content id of an attachment in the DIME message, will be recognized.

Author:
Oliver Treichel
